				<td colspan="2"><span>couple nights ago, my friend tell me to come to PoV wasteland and see a crazy bard on action. 
<br />
i went there and say a bard running in perfect big cirlce with some golem, arachnae and such running behind him.
<br />
i am sure he was singing runing song and DoT mobs behind him.
<br />
my friend, told me that the bard has been there for 9 hours straight doing this. he added, the bard might be afk since he didnt do anything other than running and dotting the mob.
<br />
from what i saw, he is using macro to do that stuff. probably illegal. 
<br />
anyone know how he do this?
<br />

<br />
he was using TDoK, sing running song, sing some DoT.
<br />
my question is, even though i can Dot kite a single mob till it dies, i have to look at the other mob and trget it, since without line of sight, f8 didnt work. how did he do it? what script did he use? is it legal?
<br />

<br />
i dont suggest anyone to do this. I like to play what i pay every month. that bard, he pays, but he put script and went afk. no fun at all.
<br />

<br />
