<br />

<br />
You'd see that over and over and over and over. It would be funny for about the first minute or two, then annoying as the corpses stacked up at the soulbinder.
<br />

<br />
Anyhow, I really hope that anyone out there thinking about using a macro system reads these forums before doing so. </span></td>
